Listen, darling, there's a lovely little
spot nearby. Care to visit with me?

rows.label: kizunainn068_msg002
rows.name:
It's called the Airborne Throne.
The innkeeper told me about it.

rows.label: kizunainn068_msg003
rows.name:
It'll be so much fun if we go there...
just the two of us.
